        Method to add university
        Parameters:
        state - the state where the school is located
        location - what type of area is the school located at
        control - the type of school (e.g. private)
        numOfStu - number of students attending school
        perFem - percentage of females attending
        satVerbal - average SAT Verbal score
        satMath - average SAT Math score

        perAdmit - the percentage of admitted students
        perEnroll - the percentage of students enrolled after applying
        control - the control of school amount
        academicScale - the scale of academic life on campus
        socialScale - the scale of social life on campus
        lifeScale - the scale of life on campus
        popMajor - a list of popular majors at university
        Returns:
        true if add successfully, otherwise false
